database_registration.title: Government Database Registration
database_registration.description: All documents are registered in official government databases and pass all verification systems including border control, airport security, and online verification portals.

faq_section.title: Frequently Asked Questions
faq_section.subtitle: Get answers to common questions about this product

questions.question: How long does processing take?
questions.answer_template: Standard processing time is {processing_time}. Express options are available for urgent orders.

questions.question: Is this document registered in government databases?
questions.answer: Yes, all our documents are fully registered in the respective government databases and pass all verification checks.

questions.question: What payment methods do you accept?
questions.answer: We accept cryptocurrency, wire transfers, and other secure payment methods. Full details provided during checkout.

questions.question: Do you offer worldwide shipping?
questions.answer: Yes, we ship worldwide using secure, tracked shipping methods. Delivery times vary by location.

questions.question: What if my document is damaged during shipping?
questions.answer: All products are fully insured. We will replace any damaged items at no additional cost.

worldwide_delivery.title: Worldwide Delivery
worldwide_delivery.description: We ship to over 180 countries worldwide using secure, tracked shipping methods. All packages are discreetly packaged and fully insured.

expert_support.title: Expert Support
expert_support.description: Our support team is available 24/7 to answer your questions and assist with your order. Contact us anytime via secure channels.
